divs: Sighting DetailsI went to my back yard to smoke a cigarette I sat on my porch and as I looked up, I seen a UfO from my backyard, it was circular, and seemed to be translucent with a gel like substance that covered it, lights were perfectly spaced around it, it moved through the sky like a jellyfish would through water, it was 200-400 feet in diameter, please call I have nothing too gain or lose I just need to talk to someone that believes...cell#720-470-8710 my name is Francesco. The amazing thing about this circumstance is that a witness is backing me up I went to the corner and this man seen it as well and he is willing to talk as well...............Please Call!!!I have nothing to hide.
